{"type":"message","id":"ac999555","parentId":"94eb3fb7","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:59:30.235Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 00:59 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态：\n1. 企业数字化转型政策与市场动态（2026年）\n2. 智能安防行业趋势\n3. 网络系统集成市场动态\n4. IT运维服务行业发展\n\n请搜索最新信息，整理3-5条关键信息。返回结构化的关键信息摘要。"}],"timestamp":1773939570231}}
{"type":"message","id":"bae030d6","parentId":"ac999555","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:59:35.176Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为子代理，搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态。需要搜索四个方面：\n1. 企业数字化转型政策与市场动态（2026年）\n2. 智能安防行业趋势\n3. 网络系统集成市场动态\n4. IT运维服务行业发展\n\n我需要搜索最新信息，整理3-5条关键信息，返回结构化的关键信息摘要。\n\n让我使用web-search技能来搜索这些信息。","thinkingSignature":"3a729d4449bbe4ba17e541fbd35a12f1e08285277d295a0573cb258314a433f4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0n070jcwjgce_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.agents/skills && ls -la | grep -E \"web|search\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":129,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30739,"totalTokens":30985,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001548,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0036886799999999997,"total":0.0038785799999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773939570233}}
